description.en:
A recap of stereo techniques: XY, AB, MS, Blumlein, ORTF;
History of stereo techniques;
Stereo arrays, focusing on new techniques and its variations, such as the OCCO;
Decca Three and its variations;
Stereo array techniques, including how each reproduces information that originates behind and beside the array;
Stereophony;
The concept of critical distance (Dc) and how this determines in part where microphones must be positioned to record a source intelligibly;
The importance of accurately capturing lateral reflections, ambience, and reverberation in a performance space;
Intensity stereo;
Comparing Stereo Arrays;
Location recording;
Choosing and positioning a stereo array based on its stereophonic recording angle;
How much microphone selection and positioning influences listeners’ impression; 
Creative and unconventional/uncommon recording techniques

description.et:
Stereotehnikate kokkuvõte: XY, AB, MS, Blumlein, ORTF;
Stereotehnikate ajalugu;
Stereo lahendused, keskendudes uutele tehnikatele ja selle variatsioonidele, nagu OCCO;
Decca Three ja selle variatsioonid;
Stereo lahenduste tehnikad;
Stereofoonia;
Kriitilise kauguse (Dc) mõiste 
Külgpeegelduste, atmosfääri ja kaja täpse jäädvustamise tähtsus salvestamise keskkonnas;
Stereo to mono konversioon;
Stereo lahenduste võrdlemine;
Erinevate keskkondade salvestamine;
Stereo lahenduse valimine salvestamisel ja selle paigutamine stereofoonilise salvestusnurga alusel;
Kui palju mõjutab mikrofoni valik ja paigutus kuulajate muljet; 
Loomingulised ja ebatavalised/ebatavalised salvestustehnikad
